title: PBE won't launch
body: I want to start PBE but it is not working even if I run as admin. I click on it and the LOL symbol appears but it won't go to the launcher. Any ideas?

replies.body:
Your connection to the PBE servers (which are in the US) is probably poor. This can typically be resolved by working through the solutions listed in our [connection guide](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues).

Let me know if this helped.
